  "data": {
    "Name": "Drogon - Decision Gate 2 DG2 Concept Select",
    "Description": "DG2 Concept Select for the Drogon field development, aligned with the official Drogon FMU model (equinor/fmu-drogon tutorial 24.3.1). Volantis Group (Valysar, Therys, Volon formations) across 7 fault-bounded reservoir regions (WestLowland, CentralSouth, CentralNorth, NorthHorst, CentralRamp, CentralHorst, EastLowland). 250 FMU realisations with one-by-one sensitivity design, OPM Flow simulator. 4 producers (A1–A4), 2 water injectors (A5–A6). STOIIP P50 45.4 MSm³, EUR P50 10.4 MSm³ oil, RF P50 33.5%. Recommended concept: subsea tie-back to FPSO with 2×4-slot templates, 6 active wells + 2 contingent infill. NPV@10% 520 MUSD, CAPEX 8,500 MNOK, first oil 2028-H1.",
    "ProjectName": "Drogon Field Development",
    "DecisionLevelID": "dev:reference-data--DecisionLevel:DG2:",
    "ApprovalStatusID": "dev:reference-data--DecisionApprovalStatus:Pending:",
    "DecisionDueDate": "2026-06-30",
    "DecisionSummary": "Approve subsea tie-back development concept. Two 4-slot templates (8 slots + 2 contingent), 4 producers (A1–A4) + 2 injectors (A5–A6) targeting full Volantis Group (Valysar, Therys, Volon) across 7 regions. STOIIP P50 45.4 MSm³ (P90 33.8, P10 59.4). EUR P50 10.4 MSm³ (RF 33.5%). 250 FMU realisations with one-by-one sensitivity (drogon_design.ert). First oil target 2028-H1. Proceed to DG3 FEED.",
    "RiskAssessmentDocument": "dev:work-product-component--Document:Drogon-SRA-DG2-Report:1",
